|[[李白|李白]] || 《甘肅日報》指出，據南韓首爾大學歷史系教授金秉德考證，李白是韓國人的後代。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.chinatimes.com/mainland/0,5245,110505x112010051900097,00.html|title=首爾教授：李白是韓國人 大陸學者:離譜|date=2010-05-19|publisher=中國時報|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521091948/http://news.chinatimes.com/mainland/0,5245,110505x112010051900097,00.html|archivedate=2010-05-21}}</ref>但是首爾大學沒有歷史系，也無金秉德此人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.donga.com/Column/3/04/20100519/28450402/1|title=[기자의 눈/이헌진]혐한류 날조 기사 퍼나르는 中관영매체들|date=2010-05-01|publisher=東亞日報|accessdate=2010-05-19|archive-date=2018-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326202438/http://news.donga.com/Column/3/04/20100519/28450402/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20100520000804-260108?chdtv|title=李白韓人？駐台韓代表部澄清|date=2010-05-20|publisher=中國時報}}</ref>
